snippet.title: Legacy Gaming
snippet.description:
Join Codiak and Livid and be part of a fast growing positive gaming community.
With in-depth coverage of the games you care about, and high-quality videos you'll always walk away with a little more knowledge about the games that you love.

Looter Shooters, RPGs, Story Driven Single Player experiences, Open-World Games, Survival Games, and more. We love ALL things gaming and strive to be objective in our review process.

Be part of the conversation and Join Legacy Gaming today!

[Reach Out]
Business - codiak@legacygaming.gg
Discord - https://discord.gg/legacygaming 
Twitter - twitter.com/LegacyGaming_US

[Support The Channel]
Become A Member - https://bit.ly/32nfMLQ

Footage may not be used by any outside party under no circumstances unless given written consent from Legacy Gaming.

Leave A Legacy!
